strings:
<voice_0x010018DB><se_high>Jessica: Great Alexandra...grant us your blessing,
and watch over us until the end of our days.
<voice_0x010018DC><se_high>Jessica: I can't believe how much has happened since I first met you and the others here.

<voice_0x010018DD><se_high>Jessica: You know, I really wasn't sure about you at first.
I thought you were a bit of a pushover,
always doing what other people told you.
<voice_0x010018DE><se_high>Jessica: But then when you saved me from Rhapthorne's curse, I started to see you in a different light.
<voice_0x010018DF><se_high>Jessica: Before I knew it, I felt like I could rely on you like I used to rely on Alistair.
<voice_0x010018E0><se_high>Jessica: And the longer we spent together, the more my feelings grew...until I realised I'd fallen for you.

<voice_0x010018E1><se_high>Jessica: Ha ha, it all seems like a lifetime ago already.
Just too much has happened.
<voice_0x010018E2><se_high>Jessica: Anyway, we should be getting back to the house. To OUR house.
<voice_0x010018E3><se_high>Jessica: I am so happy right now.
<voice_0x010018E5><se_high>Jessica: ...from now on, I can come to you for everything. Right...hubby?
